## Firebase React Project Workflow
- create components,context,firebase,hooks,pages, folder
- each page/component styled with css modules
- create seperate hook for each logic
 - first create sign up hook
 - create global context to reflect user state in app
 - create logout, since sign up automatically sings use
 - use cleanup functions for async work
- firebase auth , passes user token on each request, which can be used to protect routes, store user in react context
- add filter rules with fb queries and fb rules
